description: Lily`s Solrock is a Tripokalon Performer who participated in the Hyakkoku Tripokalon Tournament in the Kalos region. It was eliminated in the first quiz question round when it was matched up against Serena`s Pancham and Nene`s Farfetch`d and was unable to return the ball back to Lily in time to answer any of the quiz questions.
name: Solrock (Lily)
